---
---
<section id="services" style="background-color: var(--color-secondary); padding: var(--space-2xl) 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div class="section-pad" style="padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0;">
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
      <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl);">Our <span class="text-accent">Systems</span></h2>
      <p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: var(--text-lg); max-width: 65ch;">Effective business automation solutions that leverage modern APIs and AI logic to help you grow with zero administrative drag.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-3">
      
      <!-- Sales System -->
      <div class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: #DBEAFE; width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20"></path><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Sales Systems</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">
          Automated, AI-driven lead acquisition systems that book sales meetings directly on your calendar. Experience a powerful return on investment by entirely removing the human SDR bottleneck.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-main); font-weight: 500; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Omni-channel outreach sequencing</li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> HubSpot & Salesforce deep integration</li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> AI-personalized email drafting (ChatGPT API)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Marketing System -->
      <div class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: #DBEAFE; width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="3 11 22 2 13 21 11 13 3 11"></polygon></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Marketing Systems</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">
          Finished, hands-off inbound marketing systems that nurture leads autonomously. We orchestrate complex multi-step logic to ensure your brand runs 24/7.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-main); font-weight: 500; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Custom Make.com workflow architecture</li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Automated content generation logic</li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Zapier webhooks and triggers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Project Management -->
      <div class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: #DBEAFE; width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Project Management</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">
          Take advantage of best-practice, high-ROI project management systems. We centralize data lakes and unify platforms so nothing falls through the cracks.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-main); font-weight: 500; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Custom Airtable schema design</li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Native REST API script integration</li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Python-based internal data scrubbing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
